ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectUkraine Goods Remission Order
PrecisUKRAINE GOODS REMISSION ORDER in order to remit customs duties paid or payable under the CUSTOMS TARIFF, as well as anti-dumping and countervailing duties paid or payable under the SPECIAL IMPORT MEASURES ACT, for all goods originating in Ukraine and imported into Canada for a period of one year.
